readable.content: Four people posing for a photo in front of a pond . Four young people stand near a bike with two flags on it . This is a picture of three young men , dressed in suits with one on a bike , and of a young lady wearing a white dress . Three boys in suits and sashes and a girl in a dress in sash in a field . Three smartly dressed man and woman are standing beside a bicycle on the grass .
